{"tid":1693382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】暴動罪過往點打甩?","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:24:04.000Z","uid":78715,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab3dfa86b8fbdea09b790b396d24056d7c09702","tid":1693382,"uid":78715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"香城online大家打到 呢個階段 好多手足陣亡左。<br />\n <br />\n俾狗咬既義士好多都要面對一堆控罪， 雖然大家都唔好對法庭有咩期望，但睇返魚蛋革命紀錄，告左都唔等於無得打，所以做左呢個整合，希望幫到義士請最好既律師打。<br />\n <br />\nFC咗一堆律師，魚蛋之後打過暴動案既往績畀各位手足參考<br />\n <br />\n真係打甩過既有以下：<br />\n <br />\n葉謝鄧律師行 伙拍  石書銘大律師<br />\n鄺文輝律師行 伙拍  陳偉彥大律師<br />\n丘煥法律師行 伙拍  王國豪大律師<br />\n何謝韋律師行 伙拍  馬維騉大律師<br />\n范黃曹律師行 伙拍  姚本成大律師<br />\n鄺文輝律師行 伙拍  王國豪大律師<br />\nPS:伍展邦律師行就未試過打甩，判得最重。<br />\n <br />\n手足加油！"},{"pid":"27b8fb6dabc5a793a20c4d5febc6fc96ccc08bdc","tid":1693382,"uid":78715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce5e74442b6b37637b48eaf8ed168ea69790e6e","tid":1693382,"uid":333972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276160e2b7747cb8b645511ac3bba2feff44928a","tid":1693382,"uid":63304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6702f7c4d66e18e8e19a7153e6161b66f312985","tid":1693382,"uid":118945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1